com.interpss.opf.datatype

Interface BaseOpfConstraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseOpfConstraintImpl

    public interface BaseOpfConstraint
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Opf Constraint'. Base Opf constraint

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Desc
    • Cst Type
    • Upper Limit
    • Lower Limit
    • Solution Value
    See Also:
    OpfDatatypePackage.getBaseOpfConstraint()
